questions.question_text:
You issued this command:
RMAN> BACKUP RECOVERY FILES;
Which two are true? (Choose two.)

discussion.content:
DE 
By adding the subclause destination to the backup recovery files command, you can specify a disk channel as the location for the backing up of the recovery area files:
RMAN> backup recovery files to destination '/u01/app/oracle/backup';

Selected Answer: AC
